OL,3,C"We think it will kill her":Families
OL,4,Cin shock after care home announces
OL,5,Cclosure
OL,7,FGranada Reports correspondent Tim
OL,8,FScott spoke to family members about
OL,9,Fthe future of their loved ones.
OL,11,FFamilies of people living in a care
OL,12,Fhome that's due to close say that
OL,13,Fforcing their loved-ones to leave and
OL,14,Ffind new accommodation will put them
OL,15,Funder unbearable strain.
OL,17,FThe management of Acorn Lodge in
OL,18,FFailsworth, Greater Manchester
OL,19,Fannounced last week that they've sold
OL,20,Fthe building to be renovated and re-
OL,21,Fpurposed.
