OL,7,FAll of the current 68 residents, many
OL,8,Fwith dementia, will have to live
OL,9,Felsewhere.
OL,11,FSharon Freakes' 88 year-old father who
OL,12,Fhas dementia has lived at Acorn Lodge
OL,13,Ffor nine months.
OL,15,FShe said: "Everyone is just hurting
OL,16,Finside, thinking how are we going to
OL,17,Ftell them? It's just unthinkable."
