OL,7,FHer father currently needs a special
OL,8,FElderly Mentally Infirm (EMI) bed at
OL,9,Fthe unit because he has a particular
OL,10,Fadvanced stage of dementia.
OL,12,FShe worries that they'll struggle to
OL,13,Ffind him these resources elsewhere.
OL,15,FLinda Walsh and Barbara Hatch are
OL,16,Fsisters whose mother lives at Acorn
OL,17,FLodge.
