OL,7,FIn a statement, the home's management
OL,8,Fsaid: "We have made Oldham Council
OL,9,Faware that we, as owners of the Acorn
OL,10,FLodge Nursing Home, have agreed a sale
OL,11,Fof Acorn Lodge to Exemplar Health Care
OL,12,Fwho plan to extensively refurbish and
OL,13,Frenovate the home and re-open it as a
OL,14,Fspecialist home for adults living with
OL,15,Facquired brain injuries, neurological
OL,16,Fconditions, dementia and physical
OL,17,Fdisabilities.
