OL,3,C"We think it will kill her":Families
OL,4,Cin shock after care home announces
OL,5,Cclosure
OL,7,F"Funding for the health and social
OL,8,Fcare system in recent years has not
OL,9,Fkept pace with theJrate of inflation
OL,10,Fand the other costs of day-to-day
OL,11,Fliving.
OL,13,F"These will, as is evidenced from the
OL,14,Flarge number of other closures in the
OL,15,Farea, start to have an impact in the
OL,16,Ffuture. It was for this reason that we
OL,17,Fhad made the difficult decision to
OL,18,Fsell the home, before any financial
OL,19,Fstruggles started and whilst we could
OL,20,Fstill ensure the highest quality of
OL,21,Fservice and care."
