OL,7,FOldham Council said that while they
OL,8,Fare frustrated at the short notice of
OL,9,Fthe announcement to close Acorn Lodge,
OL,10,Fthey can't prevent it being closed and
OL,11,Fthey're now working to try and rehome
OL,12,Fresidents as quickly as possible.
